      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,13 @@\n+# Upgrading Dependencies\n+\n+Upgrade all dependencies:\n+\n+```sh\n+uv lock --upgrade\n+```\n+\n+Commit:\n+\n+```sh\n+git add uv.lock && git commit -m \"Upgrade dependencies\"\n+```"
